            <title><![CDATA[GungHo Online Entertainment to debut new title at TGS 2025]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/gungho-online-entertainment-to-debut-new-title-at-tgs-2025</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/gungho-online-entertainment-to-debut-new-title-at-tgs-2025.1306218/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p><a title="Companies > GungHo Online Entertainment [439 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/gungho-online-entertainment">GungHo Online Entertainment</a> will debut a new title at Tokyo Game Show 2025, which will run from September 25 to 28 at Makuhari Messe in Chiba, Japan. <span id="more-995144"></span></p><p>The new title will be playable for the first time at the GungHo booth. Players who try the demo will receive an original novelty item, and those who share photos or videos of their gameplay on social media will receive an even more special original novelty item.</p><p>The official website and social media accounts for the new title will open soon.</p><p>The press release teases, “What genre is it? And for what platform? Find the answers at Tokyo Game Show 2025.”</p><p>Stay tuned.</p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/gungho-online-entertainment-to-debut-new-title-at-tgs-2025]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Nioh 3 launches February 6, 2026, Amazon Japan listings reveal]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/nioh-3-launches-february-6-2026</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/nioh-3-launches-february-6-2026-amazon-japan-listings-reveal.1306200/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>A look at the box art and Treasure Box edition.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Dark Sengoku <a title="Genres > Action RPG [1,794 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/rpg/action-rpg">action RPG</a> sequel <em><a title="Games > Nioh 3 [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/nioh-3">Nioh 3</a></em> will launch for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,435 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a> and <a title="Platforms > PC [24,326 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3681010/Nioh_3/" target="_blank">Steam</a> on February 6, 2026, according to newly posted listings on Amazon Japan. <span id="more-995059"></span></p><p>The listings are for the game’s <a href="https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B0FSC7XY5N" target="_blank">standard</a> and <a href="https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B0FSD2T42N" target="_blank">Treasure Box</a> editions. Both listings include a release date of February 6, 2026.</p><p>Here is the previously not revealed box art:</p><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Nioh-3-Date-Leak_09-24-25_001.jpg"></a></figure><p>The <a title="Companies > Treasure [14 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/treasure">Treasure</a> Box edition includes a B5-size official art book, a selection soundtrack CD, an original desk mat, and an Sunekosuri fur ball key chain:</p><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Nioh-3-Date-Leak_09-24-25_002.jpg"></a></figure><!-- AD: content -->
        <p>Since publisher <a title="Companies > Koei Tecmo Games [3,094 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/koei-tecmo-games">Koei Tecmo</a> or developer <a title="Companies > Team NINJA [656 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/koei-tecmo-games/team-ninja">Team NINJA</a> have yet to publish an official announcement, and retail listings are not up at any other Japanese retailer, it is possible Amazon posted the listing early in error, ahead of an announcement at <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/state-of-play-set-for-september-24-featuring-35-minutes-of-updates-from-playstation-studios-and-partners">today’s State of Play</a> or <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/event/tokyo-game-show-2025/">this week’s Tokyo Game Show 2025</a>.</p><p>Thanks, <a href="https://twitter.com/Renka_schedule/status/1970717557629047193" target="_blank">@renka_schedule</a>.</p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/nioh-3-launches-february-6-2026]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
